<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>MiniWinTools - 무료 윈도우 미니앱</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0b0d10;
      --panel: #151922;
      --panel-soft: #1b2130;
      --text: #f4f7fb;
      --muted: #9aa4b2;
      --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --accent: #6ee7ff;
      --accent-2: #8b5cf6;
      --radius: 22px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(110,231,255,0.14), transparent 32%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(139,92,246,0.18), transparent 30%),
        var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .wrap {
      width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      background: rgba(11, 13, 16, 0.72);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .nav {
      height: 72px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .logo-mark {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(110,231,255,0.35);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 22px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 92px 0 72px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 56px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(44px, 7vw, 82px);
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.07em;
    }

    .lead {
      margin: 24px 0 34px;
      max-width: 620px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 19px;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 52px;
      padding: 0 22px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-weight: 750;
      transition: transform .18s ease, border-color .18s ease, background .18s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      color: #071014;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(110,231,255,0.18);
    }

    .btn-ghost {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--text);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }

    .mockup {
      padding: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 30px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), rgba(255,255,255,0.03));
      box-shadow: 0 30px 90px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
    }

    .window {
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: #0f131b;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .window-top {
      height: 46px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 0 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }

    .dot {
      width: 11px;
      height: 11px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.28);
    }

    .window-body {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .fake-line {
      height: 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .fake-line.big {
      height: 92px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(110,231,255,0.22), rgba(139,92,246,0.18));
    }

    section {
      padding: 56px 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .section-title h2 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    }

    .section-title p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 26px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), rgba(255,255,255,0.025));
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 24px;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .meta {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .card p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .feature {
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .feature strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .safety {
      padding: 28px;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      border: 1px solid rgba(110,231,255,0.2);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(110,231,255,0.08), rgba(139,92,246,0.08));
    }

    .safety ul {
      margin: 14px 0 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    footer {
      padding: 36px 0 50px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .hero {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        padding-top: 64px;
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: none;
      }

      .grid,
      .features {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .actions .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="wrap nav">
      <a class="logo" href="#">
        <span class="logo-mark"></span>
        <span>MiniWinTools</span>
      </a>

      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#apps">Apps</a>
        <a href="#why">Why</a>
        <a href="#safety">Safety</a>
        <a href="mailto:your@email.com">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="wrap hero">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">Windows 10 / 11 · Portable EXE</div>
        <h1>무료 윈도우 미니앱.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          설치 없이 바로 실행하는 작은 Windows 도구들입니다.
          광고, 로그인, 복잡한 설정 없이 필요한 기능만 담았습니다.
        </p>

        <div class="actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="downloads/app1.zip" download>App 1 다운로드 · 1MB</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="downloads/app2.zip" download>App 2 다운로드 · 4MB</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mockup">
        <div class="window">
          <div class="window-top">
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <span class="dot"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="window-body">
            <div class="fake-line big"></div>
            <div class="fake-line" style="width: 88%;"></div>
            <div class="fake-line" style="width: 64%;"></div>
            <div class="fake-line" style="width: 74%;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section id="apps">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>다운로드</h2>
          <p>작고 가벼운 무료 Windows 앱 2개를 제공합니다.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>App 1 이름</h3>
            <div class="meta">v1.0.0 · 1MB · Windows 10/11 · Portable</div>
            <p>
              여기에 App 1 설명을 적으세요. 예: 반복 작업을 빠르게 처리하는 작은 유틸리티입니다.
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="downloads/app1.zip" download>다운로드</a>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>App 2 이름</h3>
            <div class="meta">v1.0.0 · 4MB · Windows 10/11 · Portable</div>
            <p>
              여기에 App 2 설명을 적으세요. 예: 파일이나 텍스트를 간단하게 정리하는 도구입니다.
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="downloads/app2.zip" download>다운로드</a>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="why">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>가볍게 만들었습니다</h2>
          <p>불필요한 기능을 줄이고 바로 실행할 수 있게 구성했습니다.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
          <div class="feature">
            <strong>무설치</strong>
            zip을 풀고 exe를 실행하면 됩니다.
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <strong>무료</strong>
            개인 사용자를 위한 무료 앱입니다.
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <strong>로그인 없음</strong>
            계정 생성이나 가입이 필요 없습니다.
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <strong>광고 없음</strong>
            앱 안에 광고를 넣지 않았습니다.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="safety">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="safety">
          <h2>보안 안내</h2>
          <p>
            개인 개발자가 무료로 배포하는 Windows 앱입니다.
            실행 시 Windows에서 “알 수 없는 게시자” 경고가 표시될 수 있습니다.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>설치가 필요 없는 포터블 앱입니다.</li>
            <li>불필요한 권한을 요구하지 않습니다.</li>
            <li>가능하면 다운로드 파일의 SHA-256 해시값을 함께 공개하세요.</li>
            <li>앱 업데이트 시 버전과 변경 내용을 이 페이지에 남기면 신뢰도가 올라갑니다.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="wrap">
      © 2026 MiniWinTools. Contact: your@email.com
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
